INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("144", "1", "2016-05-18 20:38:32", "2016-05-18 20:38:32", "<p id=\"rent-a-car\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Since most travelers prefer to be in charge of their own time and movement while touring the Boka Bay instead of relying on public transportation, we provide several options for you: <em>rental cars</em>, <em>scooters</em>, <em>bicycles</em> and <em>boat</em>.</p>\n<p class=\"less\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">All our vecihles are brand new, well maintained and in excelent condition.</p>\n\n<h2>Vehicles</h2>\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/yaris1-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-158 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/yaris1-e1463433430194.jpg\" alt=\"yaris1\" width=\"125\" height=\"60\" /></a>Tianis Rent A Car offers you brand new Toyota Yaris, the best possible choice for a reliable and economic car with maximum comfort. All details and informations about prices are available at <a href=\"/rent-a-car\">rent a car page</a>.\n\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/scooter-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-159 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/scooter-e1463433481170.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"60\" /></a>Hiring a scooter is also a great way to see the Boka Bay coast. A scooter offers one complete freedom without creating parking problems, and additional benefits of being able to calmly visit all the hidden parts of a Bay.\n\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bicycle-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-160 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bicycle-e1463433531806.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"60\" /></a>\n\nMore and more visitors of Kotor find out that it\'s not only nicer and healthier to cycle, but in most cases also much faster. A cyclist can travel around without limits and never has parking problems. All our bicycles are very well maintained..\n\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/boat-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-161 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/boat-e1463433582119.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"60\" /></a>Kotor is so much more than just the cosy streets of the Old town. Kotor\'s wonderful position on the end of Boka Bay gives unique opportunities for numerous sea based activities. It is possible to hire a boat for a few hours, a day, or as long as you like.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;\">We deliver our vehicles anywhere you need in Montenegro. We also offer our driver when renting vans or cars, driver on customer account AP company terms. We can transfer you to desired destinations outside Montenegro such as Croatia or Serbia. We can also wait for your relatives or partners at the airport of Dubrovnik, Tivat or Podgorica and transfer them to the desired destination.</p>\n\n<h2>Conditions:</h2>\n<div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Minimum rental is 24 hours.</li>\n 	<li>Driver´s experience – driving licence not less then two years. Driver´s age not younger than 22.</li>\n 	<li>Car hire payable in advance, cash or with credit cards, Vat included.</li>\n 	<li>Car would be rented with full level and returned in the same condition.</li>\n 	<li>Border crossing is granted only with written company permission, otherwise is strictly forbidden.</li>\n 	<li>Insurance does not cover damages to windscreen, tyres or vehicle bottom.</li>\n 	<li>All traffic expences, parking or fees, same as penalities are on customer´s responsibility.</li>\n 	<li>Loss of keys or documents will be charged from 500 – 1000 €.</li>\n 	<li>Vehicle takeover outside of Kotor is chargeable, starting from 25 km and 1 euro per every km plus.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\nPlease <a href=\"/contact#contact\">contact us</a> for additional details about rental services.", "Vehicles", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "107-autosave-v1", "", "", "2016-05-18 20:38:32", "2016-05-18 20:38:32", "", "107", "http://localhost:8000/107-autosave-v1", "0", "revision", "", "0");
