al services</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Since most travelers prefer to be in charge of their own time and movement while touring the Boka Bay instead of relying on public transportation, we provide several options for you: rental cars, scooters, bicycles and boat.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_132\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"150\"]<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/sb2.jpg\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-132\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/sb2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Snack Bar\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Snack Bar[/caption]\r\n\r\n<a style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"/snack-bar#restaurant\">Snack Bar</a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tianis Snack bar &amp; restaurant is now officialy open. We are offering breakfast and dinner to guests at reasonable prices. It offers different breakfast menu for guests, with hot and cold options available. We are also opened for evening meals, offering a varied menu of fish and national dishes including salads, dessert, and fruit, ensuring meals are to everyone’s taste.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_150\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"150\"]<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/tara-eks-big.jpg\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-150\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/tara-eks-big-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Rafting\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a> Rafting[/caption]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"/excursions#tours\">Excursions</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our travel agency offers private tours, excursions and different programs for travellers to Kotor and Montenegro. These programs can be customized according to individual preferences and provide the opportunity to experience Montenegro in an unforgettable, intimate and personal way.</p>\r\n&nbsp;", "Home", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "5-revision-v1", "", "", "2016-05-18 19:53:05", "2016-05-18 19:53:05", "", "5", "http://localhost:8000/5-revision-v1", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("291", "1", "2016-05-18 19:53:54", "2016-05-18 19:53:54", "<p id=\"tours\" style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;\">Our travel agency offers private tours, excursions and different programs for travellers to Kotor and Montenegro. These programs can be customized according to individual preferences and provide the opportunity to experience Montenegro in an unforgettable, intimate and personal way.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The tailor made tours can be organized for any number of participants, any time for any route.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Boka Bay</h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/boka-eks-big-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-148 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/boka-eks-big-e1463520821535.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"72\" /></a>Boka Kotorska (The Bay of Kotor, Italian: Bocche di Cattaro), sometimes called Europe\'s southernmost fjord, is in fact a submerged river canyon of the disintegrated Bokeljska rijeka which used to run from the high mountain plateaus of Mount Orjen. It is an important tourist attraction in Montenegro. The bay has been inhabited since antiquity and has well preserved medieval towns. The picturesque towns of Kotor, Perast and Herceg Novi are - along with their natural surroundings - major touristic attractions. The religious heritage of the bay - its numerous Orthodox Christian and Catholic churches and monasteries - makes it one of the major pilgrimage sites of the whole region.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Skadar Lake</h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/skadjez-eks-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-260 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/skadjez-eks-e1463520464802.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"70\" /></a>Skadar lake is the largest lake on Balkan peninsula known for its beauty and very rich flora and fauna. It also holds the status of a national park. Lake Skadar and the surrounding area are rich in cultural and historic sites, known for the churches and monasteries on the islands in the lake. The area is also known for its medieval castles and fortified towns such as Žabljak Crnojevića, Obod, and the site of the printing press, which printed the first book in this part of the world in 1494, and the well-known Lesendro etc. In this unique natural reserve, rich in flora and fauna, live a large number of birds, amongst them the pelican. Lake Skadar is one of the world\'s unique bird reserves.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Rafting - River Tara</h2>\r\n<div class=\"block license\">\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/tara-eks-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-261 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/tara-eks-e1463520445842.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"70\" /></a>River rafting is a popular recreation activity in Montenegro, particularly on the Tara River. Tara Canyon, the route of the Tara River, is the deepest canyon in Montenegro and Europe, at 78 kilometers in length and 1,300 meters at its deepest. The canyon is protected as a UNESCO World Heritage Site, and is a part of Durmitor national park. One popular rafting route, follows an 18 kilometer course starting from Brstanovica, that takes approximately three hours. Other rafting routes allows enthusiasts to follow much of the dramatic Tara River Gorge - Europe\'s deepest gorge - passing near waterfalls, under bridges, near old Roman roads, and of course, through \"white water\" rougher waters for those that enjoy the most exciting of rafting trips.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Hiking</h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/hiking-eks-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-262 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/hiking-eks-e1463520413724.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"70\" /></a>Montenegrin countryside provides magnificent opportunities for trekking and walking, with trails starting from easy to challenging. Hike and explore the most renown hiking destinations and discover the hidden gems of the spectacular montenegrin mountains. TIanis offers both guided and self guided tours for hikers from all experience levels. Our guided hiking tours are perfect for those who enjoy a relaxed group environment. Our knowledgeable and experienced guides bring you through the areas they know best.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nPlease <a href=\"/contact#contact\">contact us</a> for additional details about excursions.", "Excursions", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "113-revision-v1", "", "", "2016-05-18 19:53:54", "2016-05-18 19:53:54", "", "113", "http://localhost:8000/113-revision-v1", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("292", "1", "2016-05-18 19:54:24", "2016-05-18 19:54:24", "<p id=\"rent-a-car\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Since most travelers prefer to be in charge of their own time and movement while touring the Boka Bay instead of relying on public transportation, we provide several options for you: <em>rental cars</em>, <em>scooters</em>, <em>bicycles</em> and <em>boat</em>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"less\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">All our vecihles are brand new, well maintained and in excelent condition.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"license\">Rental services</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/yaris1-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-158 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/yaris1-e1463433430194.jpg\" alt=\"yaris1\" width=\"125\" height=\"60\" /></a>Tianis Rent A Car offers you brand new Toyota Yaris, the best possible choice for a reliable and economic car with maximum comfort. All details and informations about prices are available at <a href=\"http://tianis.net/rentacar.html\">rent a car page</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/scooter-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-159 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/scooter-e1463433481170.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"60\" /></a>Hiring a scooter is also a great way to see the Boka Bay coast. A scooter offers one complete freedom without creating parking problems, and additional benefits of being able to calmly visit all the hidden parts of a Bay.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bicycle-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-160 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bicycle-e1463433531806.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"60\" /></a>\r\n\r\nMore and more visitors of Kotor find out that it\'s not only nicer and healthier to cycle, but in most cases also much faster. A cyclist can travel around without limits and never has parking problems. All our bicycles are very well maintained..\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/boat-big.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-161 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/boat-e1463433582119.jpg\" width=\"125\" height=\"60\" /></a>Kotor is so much more than just the cosy streets of the Old town. Kotor\'s wonderful position on the end of Boka Bay gives unique opportunities for numerous sea based activities It is possible to hire a boat for a few hours, a day, or as long as you like.\r\n<p class=\"red\">Please <a href=\"/contact#contact\">contact us</a> for additional details about rental services.</p>", "Rental Services", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "107-revision-v1", "", "", "2016-05-18 19:54:24", "2016-05-18 19:54:24", "", "107", "http://localhost:8000/107-revision-v1", "0", "revision", "", "0");
