/></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/tianis5-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-191 size-full alignnone\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/tianis5-th-1.jpg\" alt=\"tianis5-th\" width=\"115\" height=\"76\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Accomodation in Kotor, Tivat, Perast...</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our agency can also offer you variety of quality accommodation, not only in Kotor, but in <a href=\"/bay-of-kotor-apartments\">all parts of the Boka bay</a>. We are cooperating only with trustworthy partners, so your satisfaction and pleasure is guaranteed. Just contact us and inform us about your plans and wishes - the rest is our concern.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Click <a href=\"/bay-of-kotor-apartments\">here</a> for additional information.</p>", "Tianis Apartments", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "28-revision-v1", "", "", "2016-05-29 16:48:36", "2016-05-29 16:48:36", "", "28", "http://localhost:8000/28-revision-v1", "0", "revision", "", "0");
