INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("523", "1", "2016-06-04 19:15:25", "2016-06-04 19:15:25", "<p style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;\"><em>Travel agency Tianis</em> will help you choose ideal solution that fits your needs and suit your budget: family apartments, rooms and houses in Kotor, Tivat, Perast, Risan...</p>\r\n<p class=\"less\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Apart from our accommodation facillities, we are offering wide range of apartments, rooms, houses in the gulf of Kotor. By cooperating only with reliable partners we can guarantee that you will get exactly what you want. Let us help you!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Gulf of Kotor</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-223 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc4-th.jpg\" alt=\"acc4-th\" width=\"115\" height=\"75\" /></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-222 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc3-th.jpg\" alt=\"acc3-th\" width=\"115\" height=\"75\" /></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-221 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc2-th.jpg\" alt=\"acc2-th\" width=\"115\" height=\"75\" /></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-220\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc1-th.jpg\" alt=\"acc1-th\" width=\"120\" height=\"75\" /></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-219 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/acc-th.jpg\" alt=\"acc-th\" width=\"115\" height=\"75\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;\"><em>The Gulf of Kotor</em> is surely one of the most beautiful bays in the world. Kotor, old medieval town, lies at the very furthest end of the fjord.</p>\r\n<p class=\"less\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Winding, fjordlike inlet of the Adriatic coast, Montenegro. A fine natural harbour, it comprises four bays linked by narrow straits. The stark mountains around the bay slope steeply to a narrow shoreline on which citrus fruits and subtropical plants grow and tourist facilities have been developed\" - Encyclopedia Britannica.</p>\r\n<p class=\"less\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bay1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-322 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bay1-th.jpg\" alt=\"bay1-th\" width=\"195\" height=\"125\" /></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bay2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-323 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bay2-th.jpg\" alt=\"bay2-th\" width=\"195\" height=\"125\" /></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bay.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-324 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/bay-th.jpg\" alt=\"bay-th\" width=\"195\" height=\"125\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;\">Our travel agency offers private tours, excursions and different programs for travelers to Kotor and Montenegro. These programs can be customized according to individual preferences and provide the opportunity to experience Montenegro in an unforgettable, intimate and personal way.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The tailor made tours can be organized for any number of participants, any time for any route.</p>", "Other Apartments", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "72-revision-v1", "", "", "2016-06-04 19:15:25", "2016-06-04 19:15:25", "", "72", "http://localhost:8000/72-revision-v1", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("524", "1", "2016-06-04 19:29:07", "2016-06-04 19:29:07", "<p style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;\">Our travel agency offers private tours, excursions and different programs for travelers to Kotor and Montenegro. These programs can be customized according to individual preferences and provide the opportunity to experience Montenegro in an unforgettable, intimate and personal way.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The tailor made tours can be organized for any number of participants, any time for any route.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Currency</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Montenegrin currency is euro (EUR). 1 EUR = 100 cents.\r\nThe exchange of other foreign currencies is carried out at the counters of business banks and currency exchange offices.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Banks</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The most widespread cards are VISA, Master, Maestro and Diners, so you can carry out all kinds of monetary transactions. Foreign citizens may bring into the country unlimited quantity of foreign currencies in cache which have to be reported on the occasion of entering the country, in order to be able to take them out.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Airports</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you have chosen to arrive by air, you could get here by one of the nearby international airports, Tivat or Podgorica, or at international airport Cilipi (Dubrovnik, Croatia) that is only 16 km away from the state border, and less then 60km from Kotor.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Airport Podgorica (TGD)</strong> is located 10km outside Podgorica, capital of Montenegro, and 90km from Kotor approximately 1, 5 hours by car. There are scheduled flights to Belgrade (Serbia) as well as to various European destinations. During summer season there are many charter flights to all major European cities.</p>\r\nPodgorica airport info phone: +382 81 243 007\r\nWeb site: <a href=\"http://www.montenegroairports.com\">www.montenegroairports.com</a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Airport Tivat (TIV)</strong> is an ideal choice for our guests. It is situated less than 10 kilometers from Kotor, and it takes only 10 minutes to get from it tour hotel. There are daily flights to Belgrade (Serbia) as well as to menu European destinations. During summer season there are also charter flights to major cities of Europe.</p>\r\nTivat airport Info phone: +381 82 670 960\r\nWeb site: <a href=\"http://www.montenegroairports.com/\">www.montenegroairports.com</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Airport of Cilipi (Dubrovnik, Croatia)</strong> is 25 kilometers far from Herceg Novi (50km to our hotel) and there is organized transfer by buses to all tourist destinations in Montenegro, including Kotor.\r\n\r\nCilipi airport info phone : +385 20 773 377\r\nWeb site: <a href=\"http://www.airport-dubrovnik.hr\">www.airport-dubrovnik.hr</a>\r\n\r\nOn personal request of our guests, we could organize transfer from and to the airport (Podgorica, Tivat, and Cilipi - Dubrovnik).\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sea transfer</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There are four international ports in Montenegro: Bar, Budva, Kotor and Herceg Novi. Port of Bar is connected with Italy by regular lines Bar-Bari and Bar-Ancona.</p>\r\nPort of Bar info phone: +381 85 243 007\r\nWeb site: <a href=\"http://www.lukabar.me/index.php/en/\">www.lukabar.me</a>\r\n\r\nPort of Kotor info phone: 381 82 325 572\r\nWeb site: <a href=\"http://www.portofkotor.co.me/en\">www.portofkotor.co.me</a>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Car transportation and parking</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vehicle insurance is mandatory (carried out at the border crossing) , but Montenegro has got a special agreement with most European countries that keep out their citizens from this obligation. There is also a special \"eco\" tax (10€ per vehicle), that have to be paid on the border crossing.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For any kind of information regarding your arrival and accommodation, please don\'t hesitate to <a href=\"/contact#contact\">contact us</a>.</p>", "Tourist Info", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "318-revision-v1", "", "", "2016-06-04 19:29:07", "2016-06-04 19:29:07", "", "318", "http://localhost:8000/318-revision-v1", "0", "revision", "", "0");
